        "title": "PANDUAN MELAKUKAN TOP UP DEPOSIT SMART IN PAYS",
        "content": "<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Titillium Web&quot;;\">Panduan untuk melakukan Top Up Deposit</span></b></p><ol><li><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Titillium Web&quot;;\">Masukkan<b>&nbsp;</b><i style=\"font-weight: normal; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Titillium Web&quot;;\">username</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\">,&nbsp;</span><i style=\"font-weight: normal; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Titillium Web&quot;;\">password</span></i><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\">&nbsp;dan kode akses pada kolom yang tersedia lalu kemudian klik.</span></span></li><li><b><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Titillium Web&quot;;\"><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\">Untuk melakukan deposit anda harus terlebih dahulu mengisi data formulir pada menu&nbsp;<b style=\"font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><i><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Titillium Web&quot;;\">Keuangan --&gt; Topup --&gt; Tiket deposit</span></i></b>. Setelah mengisi data tersebut, Klik&nbsp;<b style=\"font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><i><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Titillium Web&quot;;\">‘Ambil Tiket Deposit’</span></i></b>&nbsp;untuk melanjutkan.</span></span></b></li><li><b><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Titillium Web&quot;;\"><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\">Jika pengisian sudah benar, maka akan muncul konfirmasi mengenai&nbsp;<b style=\"font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Titillium Web&quot;;\">‘Informasi Tiket Deposit’</span></b>. Setelah keluar konfirmasi tersebut, segera untuk melakukan perintah transfer ke rekening&nbsp;PT.&nbsp;Sukses Integritas Perkasa&nbsp;(xxxxx-xxxx-xxxx-x) sesuai dengan nominal yang harus ditransferkan yaitu nominal&nbsp;<b style=\"font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><i><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Titillium Web&quot;;\">Total Deposit.&nbsp;</span></i></b>Kemudian batas waktu transfernya adalah&nbsp;<b style=\"font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Titillium Web&quot;;\">3 jam&nbsp;</span></b>setelah mengambil tiket deposit.</span></span></b></li><li><b><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Titillium Web&quot;;\"><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\">Apabila transfernya sudah sesuai dengan jumlah&nbsp;<b style=\"font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><i><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Titillium Web&quot;;\">Total Deposit</span></i></b>, mohon untuk menunggu maksimal 1-30 menit, setelah itu, sistem akan&nbsp;<i style=\"font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Titillium Web&quot;;\">approve</span></i>&nbsp;secara otomatis. Dan saldo deposit anda akan terisi.</span></span></b></li><li><b><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Titillium Web&quot;;\"><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\">Selanjutnya, anda dapat mengecek status dari deposit anda pada menu&nbsp;<b style=\"font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><i><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Titillium Web&quot;;\">Keuangan --&gt; Topup --&gt; Daftar Topup.</span></i></b></span></span></b></li></ol><p class=\"NewStyle15\"><b><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Titillium Web&quot;;\">Panduan untuk melihat Buku Saldo</span></b></p><p class=\"NewStyle15\"><b><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Titillium Web&quot;;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'Titillium Web';mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12,0000pt;\">Semua status transaksi untuk </span><b><i><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Titillium Web&quot;;\">Deposit, Refund</span></i></b><span style=\"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'Titillium Web';mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12,0000pt;\">&nbsp;ataupun </span><b><i><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Titillium Web&quot;;\">Topup</span></i></b><b><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Titillium Web&quot;;\">&nbsp;</span></b><span style=\"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'Titillium Web';mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12,0000pt;\">akan muncul di buku saldo.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Titillium Web&quot;;\">Cara untuk melihatnya dengan mengikuti langkah-langkah berikuti ini :</span></p><ol><li><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Titillium Web&quot;;\">Klik menu&nbsp;<b style=\"font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><i><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Titillium Web&quot;;\">Keuangan</span></i></b></span></li><li><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Titillium Web&quot;;\"><b style=\"font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><i><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Titillium Web&quot;;\">Klik&nbsp;<b style=\"font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-style: normal;\"><i><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Titillium Web&quot;;\">Smart Wallet.</span></i></b></span></i></b></span></li></ol><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'Titillium Web';mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12,0000pt;\"><br></span></p>\r\n            ",
