      {
        "id": 29,
        "title": "Apa yang dimaksud  dengan refund?",
        "content": "<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">Proses pengembalian uang dari pembatalan penerbangan. Biaya yang ditimbulkan sesuai dengan peraturan masing-masing maskapai yang berlaku.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><i><u><span class=\"15\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">Via Email</span></u></i></b><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">&nbsp;</span></p><ol><li><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">Kirimkan pengajuan melalui To:&nbsp;<u style=\"font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; color: rgb(91, 155, 213);\">refund@smartinpays.net</span></u><span style=\"color: rgb(91, 155, 213);\">&nbsp;</span>dengan subject&nbsp;<b style=\"font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><span class=\"15\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">REFUND TICKET PESAWAT (KODE BOOKING)</span></b></span></li><li><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><span class=\"15\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">Cantumkan data dengan format sebagai berikut :</span></span></span></li><ul><li><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><span class=\"15\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">User ID :</span></span></span></li><li><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><span class=\"15\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">No. Telp :</span></span></span></li><li><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><span class=\"15\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">Kode Booking :</span></span></span></li><li><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><span class=\"15\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">Maskapai :</span></span></span></li><li><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><span class=\"15\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">Tujuan :</span></span></span></li><li><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><span class=\"15\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">Jumlah Penumpang :</span></span></span></li><li><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><span class=\"15\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">Nama Penumpang : (mohon melampirkan semua nama penumpang yang telah di isued)</span></span></span></li><li><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><span class=\"15\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">Tanggal dan Waktu yang telah diisued : (tanggal keberangkatan)</span></span></span></li><li><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><span class=\"15\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">Laporan Refund :</span></span></span></li></ul></ol><p><span style=\"font-family: Calibri;\"><span style=\"font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;\"><span class=\"15\" style=\"font-family: Calibri;\">Note : Semua data-data yang harus di isi dengan lengkap.<br></span></span></span></p>\r\n            ",
